label: Market Share
description: Compare metrics side-by-side, across a single dimension. Filter both columns of information using the filter sidebar.

query.pigql: q=load "Finance_Master";q=filter q by {{column(year_quarter_2.selection,["run_date_Year"]).asEquality("run_date_Year")}};q=filter q by {{column(year_quarter_1.selection,["run_date_Quarter"]).asEquality("run_date_Quarter")}};q = filter q by 'Franchise' == "MCGRATH";q=group q by Franchise;q=foreach q generate Franchise as Franchise, {{row(top_measures.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}};q=foreach q generate Franchise as Franchise,({{column(top_measures.selection, ["alias"]).asObject()}}/{{column(Suburb_10.result, ["sum_result"]).asObject()}}) *100 as 'Market Share %';

q=load "Finance_Master";q=filter q by {{column(year_quarter_2.selection,["run_date_Year"]).asEquality("run_date_Year")}};q=filter q by {{column(year_quarter_1.selection,["run_date_Quarter"]).asEquality("run_date_Quarter")}};q = filter q by 'Franchise' != "MCGRATH";;q=group q by franchise_name;q=foreach q generate franchise_name as franchise_name, {{row(top_measures.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}};q=foreach q generate franchise_name as franchise_name,('{{column(top_measures.selection, ["alias"]).asObject()}}'/{{column(Suburb_10.result, ["sum_result"]).asObject()}}) *100 as 'Market Share %';q=order q by 'Market Share %' desc;q=limit q 10;

q=load "Finance_Master";q=filter q by {{column(year_quarter_2.selection,["run_date_Year"]).asEquality("run_date_Year")}};q=filter q by {{column(year_quarter_1.selection,["run_date_Quarter"]).asEquality("run_date_Quarter")}};q=group q by all;q=foreach q generate {{column(top_measures.selection,["expression"]).asObject()}} as 'sum_result';

q=load "Finance_Master";q=group q by {{column(step_type_select.selection, ["value"]).asGrouping()}};q=foreach q generate {{row(step_type_select.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}}, {{row(top_measures.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}};q=foreach q generate {{row(step_type_select.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}}, ({{column(top_measures.selection, ["alias"]).asObject()}}/{{column(Suburb_3.result, ["sum_result"]).asObject()}}) *100 as All;

q=load "Finance_Master";q=filter q by {{column(Previous_Year____Qua_1.selection,["run_date_Year"]).asEquality("run_date_Year")}};q=filter q by {{column(Previous_Year____Qua_2.selection,["run_date_Quarter"]).asEquality("run_date_Quarter")}};q=group q by all;q=foreach q generate {{cell(top_measures.selection,0,"expression").asObject()}} as 'sum_result';

q = load "Finance_Master";q=filter q by {{column(Previous_Year____Qua_1.selection,["run_date_Year"]).asEquality("run_date_Year")}};q=filter q by {{column(Previous_Year____Qua_2.selection,["run_date_Quarter"]).asEquality("run_date_Quarter")}};q = group q by {{column(step_type_select.selection,["value"]).asGrouping()}};
q = foreach q generate {{row(step_type_select.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}},(sum('New_listings')/sum('Total_number_sales'))*100 as sum_List_to_sell_ratio;q=order q by sum_List_to_sell_ratio desc;

q=load "Finance_Master";q=filter q by {{column(Previous_Year____Qua_1.selection,["run_date_Year"]).asEquality("run_date_Year")}};q=filter q by {{column(Previous_Year____Qua_2.selection,["run_date_Quarter"]).asEquality("run_date_Quarter")}};q = filter q by 'Franchise' == "MCGRATH";q=group q by Franchise;q=foreach q generate Franchise as Franchise, {{row(top_measures.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}};q=foreach q generate Franchise as Franchise,({{column(top_measures.selection, ["alias"]).asObject()}}/{{column(Suburb_3.result, ["sum_result"]).asObject()}}) *100 as 'Market Share %';

a=load "Finance_Master";a=filter a by {{column(Previous_Year____Qua_1.selection,["run_date_Year"]).asEquality("run_date_Year")}};a=filter a by {{column(Previous_Year____Qua_2.selection,["run_date_Quarter"]).asEquality("run_date_Quarter")}};q = filter a by !('franchise_name' in ["MCGRATH ESTATE AGENTS", "MCGRATH GROUP"]);q=group q by franchise_name;q=foreach q generate franchise_name as franchise_name, {{row(top_measures.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}};q=foreach q generate franchise_name as franchise_name,({{column(top_measures.selection, ["alias"]).asObject()}}/{{column(Suburb_3.result, ["sum_result"]).asObject()}}) *100 as 'Market Share %';q=order q by 'Market Share %' desc;q=limit q 9;

q = load "Finance_Master";a = filter q by date('run_date_Year', 'run_date_Month', 'run_date_Day') in ["1 year ago".."1 year ago"];a = group a by ('run_date_Year', 'run_date_Quarter');a = foreach a generate 'run_date_Year' + "~~~" + 'run_date_Quarter' as 'run_date_Year~~~run_date_Quarter', {{row(top_measures.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}},"Previous Year" as Type;b = filter q by date('run_date_Year', 'run_date_Month', 'run_date_Day') in ["current year".."current year"];b = group b by ('run_date_Year', 'run_date_Quarter');b = foreach b generate 'run_date_Year' + "~~~" + 'run_date_Quarter' as 'run_date_Year~~~run_date_Quarter', {{row(top_measures.selection, [], ["expression","alias"]).asProjection()}},"Current Year" as Type;c=union a,b;c=group c by ('run_date_Year~~~run_date_Quarter', Type);c=foreach c generate 'run_date_Year~~~run_date_Quarter' as 'run_date_Year~~~run_date_Quarter',Type as Type,sum({{column(top_measures.selection, ["alias"]).asObject()}}) as Result
q=load "Finance_Master";q = group q by ('run_date_Year');q = foreach q generate 'run_date_Year' as 'run_date_Year', count() as 'count';q = order q by 'run_date_Year' desc;q=limit q 1;
q=load "Finance_Master";q = group q by ('run_date_Quarter');q = foreach q generate 'run_date_Quarter' as 'run_date_Quarter', count() as 'count';q = order q by 'run_date_Quarter' desc;q=limit q 1;
